\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Knots<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-18d1c25 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"18d1c25\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1e39503\" data-id=\"1e39503\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5044aea elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5044aea\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Square Knot<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Most Basic Knot<\/li><li>Two Throws in Opposite Directions<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Surgeon\u2019s Knot<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Initial Throw is Pulled Through Twice<\/li><li>Second Throw in Opposite Direction<\/li><li>More Stable than Square Knot<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Granny Knot<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Two Throws in the Same Direction<\/li><li>Typically Referred to as Poor Technique<\/li><li>Not as Strong as Square Knot \u2013 Can Slip<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Surgical Slip Knot<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Keeping Tension on One End the Initial Knot is Thrown Twice in the Same Direction and then Pulled Tight<ul><li>Purposeful Granny Knot<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Following Throws in Opposite Directions to Lock<\/li><li>Allows Tightening of Knot to Ensure Strength<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Aberdeen Knot<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Throws \u2013 Suture End Partially Pulled Through Loop to Form a New Loop<\/li><li>Turns \u2013 The Number of Times the Final Suture End is Passed Through the Final Loop<\/li><li>\u201cUltimate\u201d \u2013 <strong>3 Throws<\/strong> &amp; <strong>2 Turns<\/strong> (Previously Recommended 6 Throws &amp; 1 Turn)<\/li><li>Benefits: Stronger, More Secure &amp; Uses Less Suture<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-ca7e870\" data-id=\"ca7e870\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-764877d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"764877d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12452 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Suture-Knots.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Suture-Knots.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Suture-Knots-300x202.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Basic Suture Knots<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cdf74cf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" d